        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>123123123213</p><p>123123123</p><p>123213</p><p>撒2112这是我写得</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">f(x)=100x^2</script><p>$lnx$</p><pre class="line-numbers language-c" data-language="c"><code class="language-c"><span class="token macro property"><span class="token directive-hash">#</span><span class="token directive keyword">include</span><span class="token string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><span class="token keyword">int</span> <span class="token function">main</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span><span class="token function">printf</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"hellw"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span><span class="token punctuation">}</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h1 id="mak"><a href="#mak" class="headerlink" title="mak"></a>mak</h1><p>详细😂</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{eqnarray}   \sigma(z) \equiv \frac{1}{1+e^{-z}}.\end{eqnarray}</script>]]></content>
      
      
      
